1 Section 2621. There is hereby created the Tulsa Reconciliation
2 Education and Scholarship Program. The purpose of the program is to
3 provide a scholarship award to residents of the Tulsa School
4 District, which was greatly impacted both socially and economically
5 by the civil unrest that occurred in the City of Tulsa during 1921.
