11 public school district in the United States who are direct lineal
12 descendants as defined in subsection C of Section 2623 of this title
13 and who meet the criteria set forth in Sections 2623 and 2624 of
14 this title, and who are intending to pursue studies at an
15 institution of higher education in The Oklahoma State System of
